---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn more about James Hawley - CS & Economics student at the University of Virginia."
>
  <article class="about">
    <header class="about-header">
      <div class="accent-bar"></div>
      <h1>About Me</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="about-content">
      <p class="lead">
        I'm James, a Computer Science and Economics double major at the
        University of Virginia. I'm fascinated by the intersection of technology
        and markets, and I use this space to explore ideas, document projects,
        and share what I'm learning.
      </p>

      <h2>What I Write About</h2>
      <p>
        My writing spans several areas that reflect my academic and personal
        interests:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Technology:</strong> Software engineering practices, programming
          languages, and thoughts on the tech industry. As a CS major, I'm always
          exploring new frameworks, tools, and methodologies.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Economics:</strong> Market dynamics, policy analysis, and economic
          theory. I'm particularly interested in how technology is reshaping traditional
          economic models.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Book Reviews:</strong> I read widely across technology, economics,
          business, and philosophy. Here I share what I've learned and why certain
          books matter.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Projects:</strong> Technical write-ups of things I build, from concept
          to deployment. I believe in learning by doing and documenting the process.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Thoughts:</strong> Essays and responses to articles, ideas, and
          events that catch my attention.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Why I Write</h2>
      <p>
        Writing is thinking. When I write about something, I'm forced to
        understand it deeply enough to explain it clearly. This space serves
        multiple purposes: it's a way to solidify my own learning, share
        knowledge with others, and build a record of my intellectual journey.
      </p>
      <p>
        I also believe that demonstrating your thinking publicly is valuable.
        Whether you're an employer, collaborator, or fellow student, my writing
        here should give you a sense of how I approach problems and what I care
        about.
      </p>

      <h2>Background</h2>
      <p>
        At UVA, I'm pursuing both Computer Science and Economics because I
        believe the most interesting problems sit at the intersection of
        disciplines. Technology is reshaping every aspect of the economy, and
        understanding both the technical and economic dimensions gives a more
        complete picture.
      </p>
      <p>
        Outside of academics, I enjoy reading (always have a stack of books
        going), building side projects, and thinking about where technology is
        headed.
      </p>

      <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
      <p>
        If something I've written resonates with you, or if you'd like to
        discuss opportunities, I'd love to hear from you. The best way to reach
        me is through email or LinkedIn.
      </p>

      <div class="contact-links">
        <a href="mailto:james@example.com" class="contact-link">
          <svg
            width="20"
            height="20"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.5"
          >
            <path
              d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"
            ></path>
            <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"></polyline>
          </svg>
          <span>Email</span>
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://linkedin.com"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="contact-link"
        >
          <svg
            width="20"
            height="20"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.5"
          >
            <path
              d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"
            ></path>
            <rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12"></rect>
            <circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"></circle>
          </svg>
          <span>LinkedIn</span>
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://github.com"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="contact-link"
        >
          <svg
            width="20"
            height="20"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.5"
          >
            <path
              d="M9 19c-5 1.5-5-2.5-7-3m14 6v-3.87a3.37 3.37 0 0 0-.94-2.61c3.14-.35 6.44-1.54 6.44-7A5.44 5.44 0 0 0 20 4.77 5.07 5.07 0 0 0 19.91 1S18.73.65 16 2.48a13.38 13.38 0 0 0-7 0C6.27.65 5.09 1 5.09 1A5.07 5.07 0 0 0 5 4.77a5.44 5.44 0 0 0-1.5 3.78c0 5.42 3.3 6.61 6.44 7A3.37 3.37 0 0 0 9 18.13V22"
            ></path>
          </svg>
          <span>GitHub</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .about {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out;
  }

  .about-header {
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .about-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .about-content {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-content p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .about-content h2:first-of-type {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .about-content ul {
    margin-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .about-content li strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .contact-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .contact-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.875rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border: 2px solid var(--border-light);
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .contact-link::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--uva-orange), var(--uva-blue));
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .contact-link:hover {
    border-color: var(--uva-blue);
    color: white;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .contact-link:hover::before {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .contact-link svg {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .contact-link:hover svg {
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }

  .contact-link span {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
</style>
